Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and Colliers International are pleased to present 54-58 Woodfield Boulevard, Caringbah to the market For Lease.

Located on the eastern side of Woodfield Boulevard, Caringbah, this property is located only minutes from Cronulla and approximately 20 minutes from Sydney Airport and Port Botany Container Terminal. 

Woodfield Boulevard provides immediate access to Captain Cook Drive which is one of the Sutherland Shires main arterial roads.

The property was purpose built in 2010 as a food manufacturing facility and includes:

- Warehouse area: 972sqm*
- Office area: 244sqm*
- Mezzanine area: 395sqm*
- 2,035sqm* site area
- Parking for up to 17 car spaces
- Food Approved
- Grease trap & drainage
- Existing cool room, freezer and ambient areas
- High power supply (200amp per unit)
- High-clearance warehousing
- Container accessible
- IN2 Light Industrial zoning
- Two driveways in place for entry/exit providing clean truck movement
